        "title": "Pediatric Dentistry: How a Pediatric Dentist Deals with Kids and Adolescents",
        "excerpt": "Children are indeed special when it comes to dental care. That is why&nbsp;it&nbsp;so important to choose carefully when it comes to pediatric dentistry and a dental professional that specializes in pediatric care. Most importantly, children must feel at ease and any anxiety must be alleviated so that quality treatment can occur. One of the best [&hellip;]",
        "author": "Top Pinole Dental",
        "content": "<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Children are indeed special when it comes to dental care. That is why&nbsp;it&nbsp;so important to choose carefully when it comes to pediatric dentistry and a dental professional that specializes in pediatric care. Most importantly, children must feel at ease and any anxiety must be alleviated so that quality treatment can occur. One of the best ways to accomplish this goal is to work with an experienced pediatric dental care provider that understands children and adolescents and how they react to dental treatment. The good news is that there are more dental care providers that specialize in this field than ever before.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"right\",\"id\":1579,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignright size-large\"><img src=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/cute-baby-girl-brushing-teeth-top-view-1.jpg\" alt=\"Even Adolescents Can Have High Levels of Anxiety\" class=\"wp-image-1579\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5><strong>Even Adolescents Can Have High Levels&nbsp;of Anxiety<\/strong><\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>What is perhaps most unique of all when it comes to pediatric dentistry is that the dental care provider will have an office that is conducive to relaxing children and putting them at ease. Most young children and even adolescents can have high levels of anxiety at just the thought of visiting a dentist. That is why&nbsp;it is&nbsp;so important to make the experience fun, interesting and even educational. Involving children in the dental treatment process takes their mind off of anxiety. In addition, a dental office with a fun child themed environment can also work wonders in helping children deal with anxiety.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5><strong>Children Are Inquisitive&nbsp;and Always Wanting&nbsp;to Learn<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>One of the best ways to address anxiety in children and adolescents when it comes to dentistry is to engage them in the treatment that they may be receiving. Teaching children about how a cavity is filled, for example can make the entire treatment process a true learning experience. Children are inquisitive and always wanting to learn. That is why taking this approach is so effective when it comes to pediatric dentistry. Parents can get involved is well and help children to understand that dental care is a positive and good experience. Parents can also foster&nbsp;effective&nbsp;dental health with a&nbsp;good&nbsp;home dental care program.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"left\",\"id\":1578,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignleft size-large\"><img src=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/curly-blond-girl-with-smile-shows-how-brush-your-teeth-1.jpg\" alt=\"Brush and Floss \" class=\"wp-image-1578\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5><strong>Brush&nbsp;and Floss<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Teaching children the proper way to brush and floss at a very early age and making sure&nbsp;that&nbsp;they stick with their program can only serve to help them later in life. Pediatric dentistry is one of the most important parts of overall dental care because it sets the stage for a child\u2019s future dental health and wellness. With so much to offer&nbsp;it&nbsp;is clear to see why pediatric dentistry and how pediatric dentists deal with kids and adolescents is so important. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/contact\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Contact <\/a>your dentists&nbsp;in&nbsp;Pinole,&nbsp;Dr. Azadeh Hosseini, and Dr. Ghazal Hosseini at<a href=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"> Top Pinole Dental<\/a>&nbsp;for&nbsp;more information on pediatric dentistry and how it can benefit your children.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<h6>Referece: <br>\n[1] <a href=\"https:\/\/petalumaorthodontic.com\/pediatric-dentistry\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Pediatric Dentistry: How a Pediatric Dentist Deals with Kids and Adolescents<\/a><\/h6>\n<!-- \/wp:html -->",
