        "title": "What is the Function of a Dental Laboratory?",
        "excerpt": "Those who are unfamiliar with the complexities of today\u2019s modern dentistry may not be familiar with the function of&nbsp;a dental laboratory. Keep in mind that the dentist, while performing many procedures in their office, does require outside assistance and help. For example, more complicated&nbsp;and&nbsp;detailed&nbsp;crafting and work in terms of dental appliances may be performed by [&hellip;]",
        "author": "Top Pinole Dental",
        "content": "<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Those who are unfamiliar with the complexities of today\u2019s modern dentistry may not be familiar with the function of&nbsp;a dental laboratory. Keep in mind that the dentist, while performing many procedures in their office, does require outside assistance and help. For example, more complicated&nbsp;and&nbsp;detailed&nbsp;crafting and work in terms of dental appliances may be performed by an outside lab facility. In short, a dental lab is simply a standalone facility that supports dental professionals by providing customized appliances for dental patients. This includes everything from dentures to bridges and crowns as well as braces and retainers.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"right\",\"id\":1510,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignright size-large\"><img src=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/artificial-jaw-dentist-s-office-4-1.jpg\" alt=\"Strong and Reliable \" class=\"wp-image-1510\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5><strong>Strong&nbsp;and Reliable<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For example, while the dentist will take impressions of a patient\u2019s tooth, it is the dental lab that uses advanced technology visualization techniques and equipment to create&nbsp;a&nbsp;crown that will fit over the patient\u2019s tooth. This results in a perfect fit that is strong and reliable. Using precision equipment&nbsp;that&nbsp;is the latest in imaging technology results&nbsp;in better care. Another example of a dental lab and its important utility is that of creating dentures. Whether it is a full set of dentures or partials, they must be unique to the patient. A perfect fit is absolutely necessary. In the absence of a perfect fit, the patient&nbsp;may&nbsp;experience painful chewing, discomfort and even gum damage.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"left\",\"id\":1511,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignleft size-large\"><img src=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/artificial-jaw-dentist-s-office-5.jpg\" alt=\"Create Very Accurate Denture Appliances \" class=\"wp-image-1511\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5><strong>Create Very Accurate Denture Appliances<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Skilled technicians in a laboratory review the patient\u2019s jaw, mouth and gum structure details&nbsp;as a way to&nbsp;create very accurate denture appliances that will be reliable and comfortable for years and decades to come. With so much to offer it is clear to see why the dental laboratory plays a vital and important role in overall modern dentistry. As a matter of fact, few things could be accomplished without the support of these key facilities that dental care providers depend upon&nbsp;on a daily basis. To learn more about the function of a dental laboratory as well as overall dental care and services,&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/contact\/\" target=\"_blank\">contact<\/a>&nbsp;your&nbsp;Pinole dentists, Azadeh Hosseini, DDS, and Ghazal Hosseini, DDS&nbsp;at&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/\" target=\"_blank\">Top Pinole Dental<\/a>&nbsp;today.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<h6>References:<br>\n[1] <a href=\"https:\/\/www.walnutcreekdental.net\/what-does-a-dental-laboratory-do\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">What Does a Dental Laboratory Do?<\/a><br>\n[2] <a href=\"https:\/\/www.dentalimplantsolutions.net\/dental-laboratory\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">What Does A Dental Laboratory Do?<\/a><\/h6>\n<!-- \/wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->",
