        "title": "What Are All-On-Six Implants and is it a Good Choice for Me?",
        "excerpt": "There\u00a0are\u00a0many cases today where an individual may suffer a loss of all or\u00a0most\u00a0of their teeth. The good news is that there is a\u00a0type of\u00a0prostheses\u00a0designed to replace missing teeth in a highly effective way.\u00a0All-on-Six implants\u00a0offer highly reliable restorations that allow an individual to smile and chew again like normal. In essence, this is a kind of [&hellip;]",
        "author": "Top Pinole Dental",
        "content": "<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There\u00a0are\u00a0many cases today where an individual may suffer a loss of all or\u00a0most\u00a0of their teeth. The good news is that there is a\u00a0type of\u00a0prostheses\u00a0designed to replace missing teeth in a highly effective way.\u00a0All-on-Six implants\u00a0offer highly reliable restorations that allow an individual to smile and chew again like normal. In essence, this is a kind of hybrid denture that makes use of innovative dental implants. Remember that\u00a0dental implants are simply titanium rods that are surgically inserted directly into the jawbone. This results in a very strong replacement\u00a0of the tooth root\u00a0that can last for decades and even a lifetime.\u00a0<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"right\",\"id\":1445,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignright size-large\"><img src=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/toppinole-img1.jpg\" alt=\"Replace Teeth Using Six Strategically Located Dental Implants \" class=\"wp-image-1445\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5><strong>Replace Teeth Using Six Strategically Located Dental Implants<\/strong>\u00a0<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In many ways, dental implants have become the standard today when it comes to replacing missing teeth. That said, this innovative technology can also be used to create complete tooth replacement\u00a0options\u00a0in unfortunate cases where an individual has lost a large number of teeth as a result of injury or disease.\u00a0All-on-Six\u00a0is a way to replace teeth using six strategically located dental implants\u00a0in order\u00a0to secure a full arch hybrid denture. This type of dental replacement can be used for either the upper or lower teeth as an excellent\u00a0permanent solution. While the prosthesis is not readily removed by the patient, it can be removed by the dentist as necessary for cleaning or overall examinations.\u00a0<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"left\",\"id\":1449,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignleft size-large\"><img src=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/dental-prosthesis-copy.jpg\" alt=\"Endure Greater Biting Pressure \" class=\"wp-image-1449\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5><strong>Endure Greater Biting Pressure<\/strong>\u00a0<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In many ways similar to\u00a0All-on-Fours, the\u00a0All-on-Six implants\u00a0are useful in replacing an entire row of teeth\u00a0or\u00a0a complete set. The implants are simply anchors, that ensure full functionality and an attractive smile. Permanent tooth replacement is now easier and more convenient than it has ever been in the past. Using six implants rather than for simply means that the entire arch will be more stabilized and able to endure greater biting pressure. With so much to offer it is clear to see why more people than ever before considering the benefits of\u00a0All-on-Six implants\u00a0and all that they make possible. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/contact\/\">Contact<\/a> your dentists in Pinole, Azadeh Hosseini, DDS, and Ghazal Hosseini, DDS at\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/\">Top Pinole Dental\u00a0<\/a>today to learn more about All-On-Six Implants.\u00a0<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<h6>References:<br>\n[1] <a href=\"https:\/\/www.walnutcreekdental.net\/full-jaw-restoration-all-on-four-vs-denture\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Full Jaw Restoration: All-On-Four Vs Denture<\/a><br>\n[2] <a href=\"https:\/\/www.dentalimplantsolutions.net\/denture-alternatives-dental-implants-or-all-on-four\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Denture Alternatives \u2013 Dental Implants Or All-On-Four?<\/a><\/h6>\n<!-- \/wp:html -->",
