        "title": "Good Dental Health Begins with Good Food Choices",
        "excerpt": "In today\u2019s world we are exposed to so many bad foods. From fast food restaurants to processed foods such as potato chips, candy, ice cream and soda, the chances of damaging teeth and overall dental health are quite substantial. In addition, poor nutrition has grown to become a way of life for many in our [&hellip;]",
        "author": "Top Pinole Dental",
        "content": "<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In today\u2019s world we are exposed to so many bad foods. From fast food restaurants to processed foods such as potato chips, candy, ice cream and soda, the chances of damaging teeth and overall dental health are quite substantial. In addition, poor nutrition has grown to become a way of life for many in our fast-paced world. The media, online social media interaction and others seem to promote foods that are deficient in nutrition. This is a concern because these actions have a direct and lasting impact on not only overall general health but even more specifically dental health and wellness.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In today\u2019s world we are exposed to so many bad foods. From fast food restaurants to processed foods such as potato chips, candy, ice cream and soda, the chances of damaging teeth and overall oral health are quite substantial. In addition, poor nutrition has grown to become a way of life for many in our fast-paced world. The media, online social media interaction and others seem to promote foods that are deficient in nutrition. This is a concern because these actions have a direct and lasting impact on not only overall general health but even more specifically dental health and wellness.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"left\",\"id\":1273,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignleft size-large\"><img src=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/good-dental-health-begins-with-good-food-choices.jpg\" alt=\"Eating lots of fruits an vegetables can help dental health\" class=\"wp-image-1273\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>Eating Lots of Fruits and Vegetables<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When the right food choices are made, general health and dental health improves. For example, choosing to avoid foods that are artificially sweetened with table sugar can greatly improve oral health. Having healthy teeth and gums means eating and drinking in the right way. Another aspect of overall dental health involves drinking more fresh clean water. Water helps to flush away any dissolved solids that tend to cling to teeth. Eating lots of fruits and vegetables and lean sources of protein can only serve to help dental health also. Reducing the number of snacks that you eat between meals can help in the same way.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"right\",\"id\":1275,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignright size-large\"><img src=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/good-food-choices.jpg\" alt=\"Nutrition and diet choices affects dental health\" class=\"wp-image-1275\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>Nutrition and Diet Choices<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Finally, brushing twice a day and flossing while at the same time following a good home dental health program can serve to keep teeth healthy, vibrant and disease-free. When this is combined with regular routine dental visits and cleanings, the end result is great dental health going forward. When visiting with your dental care provider it is a good idea to discuss not only overall dental health but also nutrition and diet choices. Your dentist can help you to understand more specifically how nutrition and diet can have a direct impact on long-term dental health. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/contact\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Contact<\/a> your dentists in Pinole, Dr. Azadeh Hosseini and Dr. Ghazal Hosseini at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Top Pinole Dental<\/a>, today for more information on oral wellness and making the right food choices.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6} -->\n<h6>References:<br>[1] <a href=\"https:\/\/www.dentalimplantsolutions.net\/impacts-of-diet-on-oral-health-in-long-term\/\">Impacts of Diet On Oral Health In Long Term<\/a><br> [2] <a href=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/diet-effects-on-oral-health\/\">Diet Effects On Oral Health<\/a><\/h6>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->",
