        "title": "Pediatric Dentist &#8211; A Dentist For Kids",
        "excerpt": "Many new parents often ask the question of what is pediatric dentistry? The good news is that pediatric dentistry is very easy to understand and is a vital part of overall health and wellness in infants as well as adolescent children alike. A pediatric dentist is essential to the long-term dental health and wellness of [&hellip;]",
        "author": "Top Pinole Dental",
        "content": "<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"right\",\"id\":1116,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignright size-large\"><img src=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/dentistry.jpg\" alt=\"Pediatric Dentist - A Dentist For Kids\" class=\"wp-image-1116\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Many new parents often ask the question of what is pediatric dentistry? The good news is that pediatric dentistry is very easy to understand and is a vital part of overall health and wellness in infants as well as adolescent children alike. A pediatric dentist is essential to the long-term dental health and wellness of children as they grow and develop. They are professionals who have completed additional training and study in dentistry that focuses on children\u2019s dental care. Dental care for children covers a wide range of developmental issues and conditions. A pediatric dentist will offer everything from the treatment and care of cavities to dental injuries and gum disease as well as treating conditions associated with baby teeth development. For example, baby teeth that fall prematurely may require unique treatment. In most cases a dentist will provide the child with space maintainers to help ensure that adult teeth emerge normally.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>Impacted Teeth and Abscesses<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pediatric dental care focuses on the prevention and treatment of a wide range of conditions and ensures the best possible dental care for children. From dental exams to routine cleanings and x-rays, there are many aspects of childhood dental care that must be considered. Treatment can include everything from jawbone related problems to impacted teeth and abscesses as well as dental decay and even tumors. This type of dental professional may also even teach parents how to help their kids develop good habits and avoid bad habits such as thumb sucking and pacifier dependence. In short, a dental care professional that focuses primarily on pediatrics covers all aspects of dental care in children of all ages including infancy and adolescence and well into the teenage years.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"left\",\"id\":1118,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignleft size-large\"><img src=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/Pediatric-Dentistry.jpg\" alt=\"Work Closely with a Trusted Dental Care Provider\" class=\"wp-image-1118\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>Work Closely with a Trusted Dental Care Provider<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>With so much to offer it is clear to see why pediatric dentistry is so important today. Other aspects of this type of dental care include dealing with everything from improper bite to straightening teeth using braces. Even removing wisdom teeth is a focus of pediatric care. Managing gum disease and diagnosing and treating various types of medical conditions that are associated with poor oral health such as diabetes and hyperactivity are also considered. Parents can gain a lot from all the modern pediatric dentistry has to offer children. One of the best ways to take full advantage of the many benefits of pediatric care of this nature is to start early and work closely with a trusted dental care provider of your choice. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/contact\/\">Contact<\/a> your Pinole dentists for kids, Azadeh Hosseini, DDS and Ghazal Hosseini, DDS at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/\">Top Pinole Dental<\/a> today for more information.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6} -->\n<h6>References:<br> [1] <a href=\"https:\/\/www.lagunaparkdentistry.com\/do-kids-need-dental-sealants\/\">Do Kids Need Dental Sealants?<\/a><br> [2] <a href=\"https:\/\/www.happykidsdental.org\/what-does-a-pediatric-dentist-do\/\">What Does a Pediatric Dentist Do?<\/a><\/h6>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->",
