        "title": "Pick Your Shade With Professional Teeth Whitening",
        "excerpt": "One clear advantage of choosing to have teeth whitening performed in a professional dental environment is that you are able to pick your shade. Unlike doing teeth whitening at home using over-the-counter products, professional teeth whitening treatment offers more precise application and more precise results. Store-bought whitening treatments do not provide the level of control [&hellip;]",
        "author": "Top Pinole Dental",
        "content": "<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"right\",\"id\":1038,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignright size-large\"><img src=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/Professional-Teeth-Whitening2.jpg\" alt=\"Professional Teeth Whitening\" class=\"wp-image-1038\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>One clear advantage of choosing to have teeth whitening performed in a professional dental environment is that you are able to pick your shade. Unlike doing teeth whitening at home using over-the-counter products, professional teeth whitening treatment offers more precise application and more precise results. Store-bought whitening treatments do not provide the level of control that is made possible in a dental office setting. When a dental care provider does the application, the level of whitening can be precisely customized for each patient.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>Having a Uniform Teeth Whitening Experience<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All that is required is that the patient let the doctor know what shade or level of brightness they desire. A dentist can adjust the strength of the whitening gel to produce the desired results. In addition, another big advantage of choosing professional whitening treatment is that stains and discoloration are more effectively treated. In most cases a doctor will first determine what actually caused the stains in the first place. Once this has been determined, then an appropriate teeth whitening program can be applied as necessary. Having a uniform teeth whitening experience is best achieved through having professional whitening performed.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"left\",\"id\":1040,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignleft size-large\"><img src=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/Whitening.jpg\" alt=\"Safe and Secure Environment\" class=\"wp-image-1040\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>Safe and Secure Environment<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As an added bonus professional teeth whitening clearly is the safest choice today. When teeth whitening is done in a dental office it is a safe and secure environment where discomfort and errors are eliminated. Achieving a smile and greater levels of confidence and self-esteem is literally just an office visit away. Having your teeth professionally whitened will help to give you the best smile you have ever had. Finally, know that patients with increased confidence enjoy better performance on the job and in social settings. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/contact\/\">Contact<\/a> your Pinole dentists, Azadeh Hosseini, DDS and Ghazal Hosseini, DDS at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/\">Top Pinole Dental<\/a> today to learn more about professional teeth whitening with a proven track record.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6} -->\n<h6>References:<br> [1] <a href=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/tooth-whitening-in-home-vs-in-office\/\">Teeth Whitening In-Home Vs. In-Office<\/a><br> [2] <a href=\"https:\/\/www.lagunaparkdentistry.com\/holiday-time-and-protecting-dental-health\/\">Holiday Time and Protecting Dental Health<\/a><\/h6>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->",
