        "title": "Special Care for Kids&#8217; Teeth",
        "excerpt": "Making sure that children have healthy teeth is a top priority of parents today. Teeth are important to long-term oral health and wellness. Avoiding cavities as well as infection, disease and a wide range of other teeth related problems is absolutely essential and must be considered from the earliest stages of life. Children\u2019s teeth are [&hellip;]",
        "author": "Top Pinole Dental",
        "content": "<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"right\",\"id\":938,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignright size-large\"><img src=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/kids-teeth.jpg\" alt=\"Special Care for Kids' Teeth\" class=\"wp-image-938\"\/><figcaption>baby smile close<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Making sure that children have healthy teeth is a top priority of parents today. Teeth are important to long-term oral health and wellness. Avoiding cavities as well as infection, disease and a wide range of other teeth related problems is absolutely essential and must be considered from the earliest stages of life. Children\u2019s teeth are unique in that they are different than adult\u2019s teeth and as such requires special care. One of the best ways to achieve excellent results when it comes to special care for kids' teeth is to make the entire process fun. This starts with letting children pick their own toothbrush as well as letting them choose their favorite children\u2019s toothpaste.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>Proper Way to Brush and Floss<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Fortunately, today there are many flavors that make children\u2019s toothpaste a fun and exciting experience. Parents can also share videos and books about food, oral health and dental hygiene as a way to get children engaged in taking care of their teeth in the right way. Special care for kid\u2019s teeth begins with teaching them the proper way to brush and floss. It is also key to impress on children the importance of brushing and flossing twice a day or after each meal. Another big consideration when it comes to children\u2019s teeth is cavities. Children are prone to cavities especially when they eat a lot of sugar, candy or acidic foods. Another consideration when it comes to the health and wellness of your children\u2019s teeth is diet.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"left\",\"id\":936,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignleft size-large\"><img src=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/download.jpg\" alt=\"The Most Important Aspects of Long-Term Dental Health\" class=\"wp-image-936\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>The Most Important Aspects of Long-Term Dental Health<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Providing children with a wide variety of fresh fruits and vegetables is one of the best ways to encourage good oral hygiene and dental health. Foods such as apples, carrots and other types of fresh fruits and vegetables actually work like a toothbrush to keep teeth clean. These foods help to strengthen the jaw and promote the production of saliva. In short, the right types of foods will actually promote good dental health as opposed to causing cavities or periodontal disease. Finally, one of the most important aspects of long-term dental health for children is to have regular routine dental checkups and professional cleanings by a dental hygienist. These simple steps along with regular routine dental care at home will keep your children\u2019s teeth healthy and strong through all stages of life. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/contact\/\">Contact<\/a> your kids' dentist in Pinole, Azadeh Hosseini, DDS and Ghazal Hosseini, DDS at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/\">Top Pinole Dental<\/a> today for more information on special care for kids' teeth.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6} -->\n<h6>References:<br> [1] <a href=\"https:\/\/www.happykidsdental.org\/a-dentist-for-kids-pediatric-dentist-vs-general-dentist\/\">A Dentist For Kids: Pediatric Dentist Vs General Dentist<\/a><br> [2] <a href=\"https:\/\/www.lagunaparkdentistry.com\/what-is-orthodontics-and-what-is-it-used-for-today\/\">What is Orthodontics and what is it Used for Today<\/a><br> [3] <a href=\"https:\/\/www.walnutcreekdental.net\/2019\/07\/13\/how-do-dental-sealants-actually-work\/\">How Do Dental Sealants Actually Work<\/a><\/h6>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->",
