        "title": "What To Know Before Getting Dental Veneers",
        "excerpt": "Dental veneers or what are sometimes called porcelain veneers are an outstanding option when it comes to cosmetic dentistry. They are an excellent restorative solution that can easily address a wide range of dental issues. In the application of porcelain veneers, the natural tooth is file down in order to accept the porcelain veneer that [&hellip;]",
        "author": "Top Pinole Dental",
        "content": "<!-- wp:image {\"id\":557,\"align\":\"right\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignright\"><img src=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/images.jpg\" alt=\"What To Know Before Getting Dental Veneers\" class=\"wp-image-557\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Dental veneers or what are sometimes called porcelain veneers are an outstanding option when it comes to cosmetic dentistry. They are an excellent restorative solution that can easily address a wide range of dental issues. In the application of porcelain veneers, the natural tooth is file down in order to accept the porcelain veneer that is then applied to the outer portion of the tooth. The outcome is quite impressive and can have a profound effect on one\u2019s overall aesthetic appearance. That is why porcelain veneers are so popular today.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>The Quality Of Dental Porcelain Veneers<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>That said there are some things to consider prior to having this type of cosmetic dental treatment performed. For example, keep in mind that the quality of dental porcelain veneers can vary substantially from region to region and from provider to provider. Make certain that your dental care provider is experienced and has a proven track record when it comes to performing this type of unique dental procedure. Other client reviews and recommendations from those who have used a particular dental care provider can go a long way in helping you make a more informed decision.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":559,\"align\":\"left\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignleft\"><img src=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/veneers.jpg\" alt=\"What Will Be Done During The Actual Treatment\" class=\"wp-image-559\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>What Will Be Done During The Actual Treatment<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Equally important is to ask questions when it comes to the consultation phase of preparing to have dental veneers placed.  Getting all the details worked out prior to having this type of procedure is always a smart move. Your dentist will explain in detail exactly what to expect and what will be done during the actual treatment. Your dentist will also go over long-term considerations in regard to how long they can be expected to last and what the cost of replacement may be if required. Most importantly, porcelain veneers should match as close as possible the shade of your natural teeth. Your dentist will help in this regard. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/contact\/\">Contact<\/a> your Pinole dentists, Dr. Azadeh Hosseini and Dr. Ghazal Hosseini at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/\">Top Pinole Dental<\/a> for more information.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6} -->\n<h6>References:<br> [1] <a href=\"https:\/\/www.walnutcreekdental.net\/blog\/2019\/02\/04\/veneers-and-their-benefits\/\">Veneers and Their Benefits<\/a><br> [2] <a href=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/2019\/07\/19\/how-to-deal-with-a-chipped-tooth\/\">A Chipped Tooth And How To Deal With This Type Of Dental Problem<\/a><\/h6>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->",
