        "title": "Learn More About Porcelain Bridges",
        "excerpt": "There are many different types of dental bridges available today. That said one of the most popular kinds of dental bridges used in modern dentistry is something known as a porcelain bridge. A porcelain dental bridge is unique because it can help patients improve their dental health quite substantially. Most importantly, a porcelain bridge will [&hellip;]",
        "author": "Top Pinole Dental",
        "content": "<!-- wp:image {\"id\":429,\"align\":\"left\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignleft\"><img src=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/Porcelain-Fixed-Bridges.jpg\" alt=\"Learn More About Porcelain Bridges\" class=\"wp-image-429\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There are many different types of dental bridges available today. That said one of the most popular kinds of dental bridges used in modern dentistry is something known as a porcelain bridge. A porcelain dental bridge is unique because it can help patients improve their dental health quite substantially. Most importantly, a porcelain bridge will greatly improve one\u2019s smile adding to self-esteem and overall self-confidence. Porcelain bridges have many uses and purposes including being able to close a tooth gap in what would otherwise be an attractive smile.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>Improve Facial Structure By Supporting The Overall Facial Shape<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In addition, porcelain bridges help to improve overall oral functionality and allow for better speaking and eating capabilities. As an added advantage, porcelain bridges like other types of bridges also help to improve patient appearance. No less important is the fact that this type of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/porcelain-fixed-bridges\/\">dental bridge<\/a> is highly useful in supporting the patient\u2019s underlying jawbone. Increased functionality and improved appearance are all important reasons to consider porcelain bridges and all that they make possible.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":428,\"align\":\"left\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignleft\"><img src=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/khgiyrfik.jpg\" alt=\"A Porcelain Dental Bridge Can Produce Dramatic Results\" class=\"wp-image-428\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>A Porcelain Dental Bridge Can Produce Dramatic Results<\/h5>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Keep in mind that a fixed dental bridge is nothing more than a dental appliance that is custom-made to suit the patient\u2019s exact needs. This is especially true for patients who have lost teeth through either injury or disease. A bridge is typically anchored on each side using a prosthetic tooth that is made of porcelain. While the concept is rather simple, a porcelain dental bridge can produce dramatic results for those wishing to improve their outward appearance. All that is really required is a natural tooth on either side of the bridge and the end result can be quite stunning. Whether a patient has lost teeth to decay, trauma or extraction, a porcelain bridge is a smart solution for patients of just about any age. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/contact\/\">Contact<\/a> your dentist in Pinole, Dr. Azadeh Hosseini and Dr. Ghazal Hosseini at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/\">Top Pinole Dental<\/a> today for more information on porcelain crowns.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6} -->\n<h6>References:<br> [1] <a href=\"https:\/\/www.walnutcreekdental.net\/blog\/2019\/03\/29\/porcelain-bridges-and-how-they-help\/\">Porcelain Bridges and How They Help<\/a><br> [2] <a href=\"https:\/\/www.toppinoledental.com\/2019\/03\/02\/tooth-extractions-and-pain\/\">Tooth Extractions and Pain \u2013 What You Need To Know<\/a><\/h6>\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->",
